text:
So, Producer!
Guess what Mimine want to say now!

I'm sure you'll get it.
There's only one producer after all.

If you don't understand what a special day
today is, Mitsumine might just cry.

Huh!? Ah, that's...! ...M-Maybe it's mine...
...I'd be embarrassed if it wasn't my birthday...!

Ufufu, great answer! Nice reaction too!
Happy birthday, I guess! Producer!
